dct_title_s: Purchasing power map of Europe : a supplement to The European markets
dct_description_sm: Chase Manhattan Bank. North Decimal Degree 71.172500. South Decimal Degree 34.890833. East Decimal Degree 31.610000. West Decimal Degree -10.418611. Includes chart: purchasing power survey [which] covers all 17 Western European countries, giving per capita income estimates . All data refer to 1962.
